<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>We have received a request to send a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>Or enter <%= edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @token) %> into your browser.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>

<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one. The link will expire in 6 hours.</p>

<p>Please do not reply to this message. The mailbox is for outbound email only.</p>

<p><strong>Commemorative Air Force</strong></p>